TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 0;


TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
Simplify and write the trigonometric expression in terms of sine and cosine:

\[ \frac{\sec t -\cos t}{\sec t}= (f(t))^2 \]

\(f(t)=\) \{ans_rule(10)\}.
EOT

$ans1="sin(t)";

ANS(fun_cmp($ans1,var=>['t']));

